  "texts": [
    "In cybersecurity exercises, the main story sets the overall context, such as a cyberattack on a financial institution.",
    "Sub-stories, which detail related incidents like internal network breaches or customer data theft, support and elaborate on the main story, adding depth and complexity to the scenario.",
    "These sub-stories (scripts), may also include incidents like attacks on third-party vendors.",
    "The story can be broken down into different scripts, each containing a series of events that form a narrative.",
    "Each script presents a part of the story from the viewpoint of one or more entities."
  ],
